event AuctionBid(uint256 indexed tokenId, address bidder, uint256 value, bool extended)
event AuctionCreated(uint256 indexed tokenId, uint256 startTime, uint256 endTime)
event AuctionExtended(uint256 indexed tokenId, uint256 endTime)
event AuctionSettled(uint256 indexed tokenId, address winner, uint256 amount)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
function auction() view returns (uint256 tokenId, uint256 amount, uint256 startTime, uint256 endTime, address bidder, bool settled)
function initialize(address _token, address _weth, uint256 _timeBuffer, uint256 _reservePrice, uint256 _duration)
